
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 07 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Pleural mass' from the dropdown menu
Then 'I describe' box is enabled and automatically selected
And 'I know' box is enabled
And 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is enabled and automatically selected
And 'Characterization II' tab is enabled
And 'Differential diagnosis' tab is enabled

When I select 'I know' box
And I am on 'Characterization I' tab
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Apical' radio button is enabled
And 'Basal' radio button is enabled

And 'Anterior' checkbox is enabled
And 'Lateral' checkbox is enabled
And 'Posterior' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fissural' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mediastinal' checkbox is enabled

And 'Differential diagnosis 1' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Size' input field is enabled
And '2nd plane' input field is enabled
And '3rd plane' input field is enabled

And 'Obtuse' radio button is enabled
And 'Acute' radio button is enabled
And 'Outwards' radio button is enabled
And 'Inwards' radio button is enabled
And 'Solitaire' radio button is enabled
And 'Multilobulated' radio button is enabled
And 'Pedunculated' radio button is enabled
And 'Well-defined' radio button is enabled
And 'Ill-defined' radio button is enabled
And 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled
